Day and night, when one gets to eat food on time, one doesnt realize what hunger pangs are.
Similarly, in day to day life, it is difficult to savour the joy of democratic rights, unless they are snatched away.
During Emergency, every citizen of the country had started getting the feeling that something that belonged to him had been snatched away.
we grew up, nurturing ourselves on the fruits of that very heritage.
And that is why the lack of it can be felt deeply by our countrymen, which is what we underwent during Emergency.
